objective: Phase 3 - Fly.io deploy config (Dockerfile, fly.toml, .env.example)
interaction:
  user_prompt: "Create Dockerfile, fly.toml for auto-sleep Fly.io deploy, .env.example"
  assistant_response_summary: |
    Created 3 files, committed as 8061708:

    apps/server/Dockerfile — multi-stage pnpm monorepo build:
    - Stage 1 (builder): node:22-alpine, copies workspace manifests + all packages src/tsconfig, installs with --frozen-lockfile, builds shared → engine → ai → server in order
    - Stage 2 (runtime): node:22-alpine, installs --prod only, copies dist artifacts from builder, CMD node apps/server/dist/index.js

    apps/server/fly.toml — auto-sleep config:
    - auto_stop_machines = "stop", min_machines_running = 0
    - Health check GET /health every 5m (long interval to allow sleep)
    - graceful_shutdown_timeout = 30s for socket.io drain
    - shared-cpu-1x, 256mb RAM
    - Deploy command: flyctl deploy --config apps/server/fly.toml (from monorepo root)

    apps/server/.env.example — documents PORT, ALLOWED_ORIGINS, CLERK_*, SUPABASE_*, SENTRY_DSN

    Also committed separately (6248183): CORS hardening in index.ts — reads ALLOWED_ORIGINS env var, /healthcheck → /health endpoint rename.
tooling:
  tools_used[2]: Write,Bash
  files_touched[5]: apps/server/Dockerfile,apps/server/fly.toml,apps/server/.env.example,apps/server/src/index.ts
tags:
